86f11d6c360888","itemReviewed":{"@id":"https://www.trustpilot.com/#/schema/Organization/zerion.io"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Jeremy Bedley","url":"https://au.trustpilot.com/users/683c51e34e662d572a2cfc21/"},"datePublished":"2025-06-11T12:31:08.000Z","headline":"Professional and responsive","reviewBody":"Professional and responsive team. Tawny Swift helped me every step of the way and returned my refund without delay. Excellent service overall.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","bestRating":"5","worstRating":"1","ratingValue":"1"},"publisher":{"@id":"https://www.trustpilot.com/#/schema/Organization/1"},"inLanguage":"en"},{"@type":"Review","@id":"https://www.trustpilot.com/#/schema/Review/zerion.io/682df51a0c11e64b74bc0ff7","itemReviewed":{"@id":"https://www.trustpilot.com/#/schema/Organization/zerion.io"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Luay","url":"https://au.trustpilot.com/users/5a5480580000ff000afd1836/"},"datePublished":"2025-05-21T17:45:30.000Z","headline":"I NEVER RECEIVED THE COINS PAID !!","reviewBody":"I PAID FOR CRYPTOS BUT IN DESPITE OF HOURS & HOURS ASKING + WAITING TO THEIR SUPPORT CHAT, I NEVER RECEIVED MY COINS PAID !!!THINK TWICE BEFORE DEALING WITH THAT COMPANY !!TRANSACTION 0xc0fedd9d379c26704f0d3c5698b9c0b4aac54aae78e09e0178f70defa818dce5","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","bestRating":"5","worstRating":"1","ratingValue":"1"},"publisher":{"@id":"https://www.trustpilot.com/#/schema/Organization/1"},"inLanguage":"en"},{"@type":"Review","@id":"https://www.trustpilot.com/#/schema/Review/zerion.io/676893869f6a8f90a5d50e1a","itemReviewed":{"@id":"https://www.trustpilot.com/#/schema/Organization/zerion.io"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Grey Seymour","url":"https://au.trustpilot.com/users/659446228114f00012ffe641/"},"datePublished":"2024-12-23T00:32:38.000Z","headline":"Zerion is the absolute best of web3, built by the best people.","reviewBody":"Zerion is the absolute best in web3, and the only crypto platform I feel safe getting my loved ones onto. Immaculately simple way to access the EVM L2-verse along with mainnet Ethereum needs, and with the launch of their own L2, super excited. What really makes Zerion special however = the people working on it. Without doxxing anyone, the support teams, the product and marketing teams, have all been incredible whether I have questions or issues or feedback. In app chat support especially shines. Can’t say enough good stuff about Zerion - the platform has honestly changed my life for the better, protected me from scams, and been a delight to use. ","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","bestRating":"5","worstRating":"1","ratingValue":"5"},"publisher":{"@id":"https://www.trustpilot.com/#/schema/Organization/1"},"inLanguage":"en"},{"@type":"Review","@id":"https://www.trustpilot.com/#/schema/Review/zerion.io/67643921a2e3320c5347d30c","itemReviewed":{"@id":"https://www.trustpilot.com/#/schema/Organization/zerion.io"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Alexander Dahmen","url":"https://au.trustpilot.com/users/676438e661528513d1e8c293/"},"datePublished":"2024-12-19T17:17:53.000Z","headline":"top wallet for multi chain support","reviewBody":"top wallet for multi chain support. incredible professional help support toohighly recomend to start your coin/token experiance with them","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","bestRating":"5","worstRating":"1","ratingValue":"5"},"publisher":{"@id":"https://www.trustpilot.com/#/schema/Organization/1"},"inLanguage":"en"},{"@type":"Review","@id":"https://www.trustpilot.com/#/schema/Review/zerion.io/675b566d439caf149baef0a0","itemReviewed":{"@id":"https://www.trustpilot.com/#/schema/Organization/zerion.io"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Jasper Sirre","url":"https://au.trustpilot.com/users/640f4c77a1216d0012df47dd/"},"datePublished":"2024-12-12T23:32:30.000Z","headline":"Nahuel is great.","reviewBody":"Nahuel is great.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","bestRating":"5","worstRating":"1","ratingValue":"5"},"publisher":{"@id":"https://www.trustpilot.com/#/schema/Organization/1"},"inLanguage":"en"},{"@type":"Review","@id":"https://www.trustpilot.com/#/schema/Review/zerion.io/674730f66effd682133c3190","itemReviewed":{"@id":"https://www.trustpilot.com/#/schema/Organization/zerion.io"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Brian Fakhoury","url":"https://au.trustpilot.com/users/64fb4a1153b615001224f5d6/"},"datePublished":"2024-11-27T16:47:18.000Z","headline":"Very honest support","reviewBody":"Very honest support, went out of there way to help with something super minor.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","bestRating":"5","worstRating":"1","ratingValue":"5"},"publisher":{"@id":"https://www.trustpilot.com/#/schema/Organization/1"},"inLanguage":"en"},{"@type":"Review","@id":"https://www.trustpilot.com/#/schema/Review/zerion.io/672cb3a722463e2512617e9f","itemReviewed":{"@id":"https://www.trustpilot.com/#/schema/Organization/zerion.io"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Consumer","url":"https://au.trustpilot.com/users/672cb39d30d0e05bbfbf4b17/"},"datePublished":"2024-11-07T14:33:43.000Z","headline":"Sebastien in the ‘chat with us’ section…","reviewBody":"Sebastien in the ‘chat with us’ section is a tireless legend. He helped me step by step with my issues and it took well over an hour.I am so relieved with the result. Thank you sooooooo Much Sebastien","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","bestRating":"5","worstRating":"1","ratingValue":"5"},"publisher":{"@id":"https://www.trustpilot.com/#/schema/Organization/1"},"inLanguage":"en"},{"@type":"Review","@id":"https://www.trustpilot.com/#/schema/Review/zerion.io/671fb96120b0c63111ec8c19","itemReviewed":{"@id":"https://www.trustpilot.com/#/schema/Organization/zerion.io"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"კრიპტო ვალუტა","url":"https://au.trustpilot.com/users/5d9c6505f3757261f657f25a/"},"datePublished":"2024-10-28T18:18:41.000Z","headline":"the best wallet very fast support","reviewBody":"the best wallet very fast support","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","bestRating":"5","worstRating":"1","ratingValue":"5"},"publisher":{"@id":"https://www.trustpilot.com/#/schema/Organization/1"},"inLanguage":"en"},{"@type":"Review","@id":"https://www.trustpilot.com/#/schema/Review/zerion.io/66c886d314fc5441aac32b42","itemReviewed":{"@id":"https://www.trustpilot.com/#/schema/Organization/zerion.io"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Joziak Ramos","url":"https://au.trustpilot.com/users/66c886ca087b623ab7bd552e/"},"datePublished":"2024-08-23T14:55:47.000Z","headline":"Amazing Support","reviewBody":"What I found most impressive was after giving up with the AI chat, the support reached out and started looking into the issue.Fast and simple, just how I prefer. awesome support.","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","bestRating":"5","worstRating":"1","ratingValue":"5"},"publisher":{"@id":"https://www.trustpilot.com/#/schema/Organization/1"},"inLanguage":"en"},{"@type":"Review","@id":"https://www.trustpilot.com/#/schema/Review/zerion.io/66c74e4c0809e6e3c58a9a45","itemReviewed":{"@id":"https://www.trustpilot.com/#/schema/Organization/zerion.io"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Dmitry Khotenov","url":"https://au.trustpilot.com/users/66c74e44e09a9e64d46a430e/"},"datePublished":"2024-08-22T16:42:20.000Z","headline":"Nice APP and very good support team!","reviewBody":"Nice APP and very good support team!","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","bestRating":"5","worstRating":"1","ratingValue":"5"},"publisher":{"@id":"https://www.trustpilot.com/#/schema/Organization/1"},"inLanguage":"en"},{"@type":"Review","@id":"https://www.trustpilot.com/#/schema/Review/zerion.io/66c4dd335808a4408f704ee4","itemReviewed":{"@id":"https://www.trustpilot.com/#/schema/Organization/zerion.io"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"AMAL Token","url":"https://au.trustpilot.com/users/659e8187d2b08a00113c026f/"},"datePublished":"2024-08-20T20:15:15.000Z","headline":"We tested more than 39 wallets","reviewBody":"We tested more than 39 wallets. This is the only wallet that we recommend to use. ","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","bestRating":"5","worstRating":"1","ratingValue":"5"},"publisher":{"@id":"https://www.trustpilot.com/#/schema/Organization/1"},"inLanguage":"en"},{"@type":"Review","@id":"https://www.trustpilot.com/#/schema/Review/zerion.io/6686d227783cff1e6c2da97d","itemReviewed":{"@id":"https://www.trustpilot.com/#/schema/Organization/zerion.io"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Trade Secret","url":"https://au.trustpilot.com/users/64c2bb27e9782d0012f30d2f/"},"datePublished":"2024-07-04T18:47:35.000Z","headline":"Love Zerion","reviewBody":"Cool team, you won't find faster support in Web3 Dapps","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","bestRating":"5","worstRating":"1","ratingValue":"5"},"publisher":{"@id":"https://www.trustpilot.com/#/schema/Organization/1"},"inLanguage":"en"},{"@type":"Review","@id":"https://www.trustpilot.com/#/schema/Review/zerion.io/663be4cc97d9fe7e9ba21687","itemReviewed":{"@id":"https://www.trustpilot.com/#/schema/Organization/zerion.io"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Crypto Sheik","url":"https://au.trustpilot.com/users/663be4c10153d23a04c5a63a/"},"datePublished":"2024-05-08T22:47:09.000Z","headline":"Talking about Zerion is easy","reviewBody":"Talking about Zerion is easy, because it is simply the best choice I made within WEB3, I use it as a wallet on my mobile device and an extension in my browser, its main benefits are security, agility and dynamism. I feel very comfortable using a solution from a team that has already been working in the blockchain market for so many years. In addition, of course, the team maintains a super active and engaged community, precisely because they are accessible and always in contact. Success always ZERION","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","bestRating":"5","worstRating":"1","ratingValue":"5"},"publisher":{"@id":"https://www.trustpilot.com/#/schema/Organization/1"},"inLanguage":"en"},{"@type":"Review","@id":"https://www.trustpilot.com/#/schema/Review/zerion.io/663a79e9176a84d3d43aaecb","itemReviewed":{"@id":"https://www.trustpilot.com/#/schema/Organization/zerion.io"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Cryptojoker","url":"https://au.trustpilot.com/users/663a79da528568d7c0a4f5c9/"},"datePublished":"2024-05-07T20:58:50.000Z","headline":"Zerion is a great app and what I love…","reviewBody":"Zerion is a great app and what I love the most is the customer service. Whenever you have issues or questions Nahuel is always there to assis. He goes above and beyond to fix any issues you may have","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","bestRating":"5","worstRating":"1","ratingValue":"5"},"publisher":{"@id":"https://www.trustpilot.com/#/schema/Organization/1"},"inLanguage":"en"},{"@type":"Review","@id":"https://www.trustpilot.com/#/schema/Review/zerion.io/6616fd8882584c7426aab007","itemReviewed":{"@id":"https://www.trustpilot.com/#/schema/Organization/zerion.io"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Hokkaidu Inu Classic","url":"https://au.trustpilot.com/users/6616fd2a7597e200123ff193/"},"datePublished":"2024-04-10T22:58:49.000Z","headline":"As a community revival project","reviewBody":"As a community revival project, we had to update our logo, and social information with Zerion. We were incredibly pleased with the professionalism, and fast-pace response we got from the team.Sincerely, a refreshing experience in the space. Thank you so much, Zerion!Much love,Hokkaidu Inu Community","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","bestRating":"5","worstRating":"1","ratingValue":"5"},"publisher":{"@id":"https://www.trustpilot.com/#/schema/Organization/1"},"inLanguage":"en"},{"@type":"Review","@id":"https://www.trustpilot.com/#/schema/Review/zerion.io/660d79310a6fdabe743ea886","itemReviewed":{"@id":"https://www.trustpilot.com/#/schema/Organization/zerion.io"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"核桃","url":"https://au.trustpilot.com/users/660d7904fa9faa0011c5fa5a/"},"datePublished":"2024-04-03T17:43:46.000Z","headline":"best wallet/tracker","reviewBody":"best wallet to track all of your internet money stuff regardless of how deep you do your onchain","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","bestRating":"5","worstRating":"1","ratingValue":"5"},"publisher":{"@id":"https://www.trustpilot.com/#/schema/Organization/1"},"inLanguage":"en"},{"@type":"Review","@id":"https://www.trustpilot.com/#/schema/Review/zerion.io/660ae13b0b86ffe911cdb006","itemReviewed":{"@id":"https://www.trustpilot.com/#/schema/Organization/zerion.io"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Anas Rguig","url":"https://au.trustpilot.com/users/660ae133109d0c00124bdd50/"},"datePublished":"2024-04-01T18:30:52.000Z","headline":"Nahuel was very useful and helped me…","reviewBody":"Nahuel was very useful and helped me properly track a coin. Fast response too !","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","bestRating":"5","worstRating":"1","ratingValue":"5"},"publisher":{"@id":"https://www.trustpilot.com/#/schema/Organization/1"},"inLanguage":"en"},{"@type":"Review","@id":"https://www.trustpilot.com/#/schema/Review/zerion.io/6606d50f40cbea0c3e091d08","itemReviewed":{"@id":"https://www.trustpilot.com/#/schema/Organization/zerion.io"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Rick Alexander","url":"https://au.trustpilot.com/users/6606d505825c8800129be2be/"},"datePublished":"2024-03-29T16:49:52.000Z","headline":"big time help setting up new token","reviewBody":"introduced a new token and Nahuel from Zerion really helped get us going. Zerion is an amazing portfolio tracker (and more) but their customer service is excellent (something that just doesn't happen in crypto)","reviewRating":{"@type":"Rating","bestRating":"5","worstRating":"1","ratingValue":"5"},"publisher":{"@id":"https://www.trustpilot.com/#/schema/Organization/1"},"inLanguage":"en"},{"@type":"Review","@id":"https://www.trustpilot.com/#/schema/Review/zerion.io/660102c5575416d6517d0b53","itemReviewed":{"@id":"https://www.trustpilot.com/#/schema/Organization/zerion.io"},"author":{"@type":"Person","name":"Sean Vitun Groves","url":"https://au.trustpilot.com/users/5830597e0000ff00