">21 May 2025</time></div></div><section class="styles_reviewContentwrapper__K2aRu" aria-disabled="false"><div class="styles_reviewHeader__DzoAZ" data-service-review-rating="1"><div class="star-rating_starRating__sdbkn star-rating_medium__Oj7C9"><img alt="Rated 1 out of 5 stars" src="https://cdn.trustpilot.net/brand-assets/4.1.0/stars/stars-1.svg"/></div></div><div class="styles_reviewContent__tuXiN" aria-hidden="false" data-review-content="true"><a href="/reviews/682df51a0c11e64b74bc0ff7" rel="nofollow" target="_self" class="link_internal__Eam_b typography_appearance-inherit__YnCNb link_link__jBdLV link_notUnderlined__y4Qsc" data-review-title-typography="true"><h2 class="typography_heading-xs__osRhC typography_appearance-default__t8iAq" data-service-review-title-typography="true">I NEVER RECEIVED THE COINS PAID !!</h2></a><p class="typography_body-l__v5JLj typography_appearance-default__t8iAq" data-service-review-text-typography="true">I PAID FOR CRYPTOS BUT IN DESPITE OF HOURS &amp; HOURS ASKING + WAITING TO THEIR SUPPORT CHAT, I NEVER RECEIVED MY COINS PAID !!!<br/><br/>THINK TWICE BEFORE DEALING WITH THAT COMPANY !!<br/><br/>TRANSACTION 0xc0fedd9d379c26704f0d3c5698b9c0b4aac54aae78e09e0178f70defa818dce5</p><p class="typography_body-m__k2UI7 typography_appearance-default__t8iAq" data-service-review-date-of-experience-typography="true"><b class="typography_body-m__k2UI7 typography_appearance-default__t8iAq typography_weight-heavy__rS52U" weight="heavy">Date of experience<!-- -->:</b> <span class="typography_body-m__k2UI7 typography_appearance-subtle__PYOVM">13 May 2025</span></p></div></section></div></article></div><div class="styles_cardWrapper__g8amG styles_show__Z8n7u"><article class="paper_paper__EGeEb paper_square__owXbO card_card__yyGgu card_noPadding__OOiac card_square___AZeg styles_reviewCard__Qwhpy" data-service-review-card-paper="true"><div><div class="styles_reviewCardInnerHeader__8Xqy8"><aside class="styles_consumerInfoWrapper__6HN5O" aria-label="Info for Grey Seymour"><div class="styles_consumerDetailsWrapper__4eZod"><div class="avatar_avatar__QtS0N avatar_orange__cIcPd" style="width:44px;min-width:44px;height:44px;min-height:44px" data-consumer-avatar="true"><span class="typography_heading-xs__osRhC typography_appearance-default__t8iAq typography_disableResponsiveSizing__z3EGy avatar_avatarName__2WZwR">GS</span></div><a href="/users/659446228114f00012ffe641" rel="nofollow" name="consumer-profile" target="_self" class="link_internal__Eam_b link_wrapper__ahpyq styles_consumerDetails__POC79" data-consumer-profile-link="true"><span class="typography_heading-xs__osRhC typography_appearance-default__t8iAq styles_consumerName__xKr9c" data-consumer-name-typography="true">Grey Seymour</span><div class="styles_consumerExtraDetails__NY6RP" data-consumer-reviews-count="2"><span class="typography_body-m__k2UI7 typography_appearance-subtle__PYOVM" data-consumer-country-typography="true">US</span><span class="typography_body-xs__IKE8N typography_appearance-subtle__PYOVM" data-lil-dot-typography="true">•</span><span class="typography_body-m__k2UI7 typography_appearance-subtle__PYOVM" data-consumer-reviews-count-typography="true">2<!-- --> reviews</span></div></a></div></aside><div class="typography_body-m__k2UI7 typography_appearance-subtle__PYOVM"><time dateTime="2024-12-23T00:32:38.000Z" class="" data-service-review-date-time-ago="true">23 Dec 2024</time></div></div><section class="styles_reviewContentwrapper__K2aRu" aria-disabled="false"><div class="styles_reviewHeader__DzoAZ" data-service-review-rating="5"><div class="star-rating_starRating__sdbkn star-rating_medium__Oj7C9"><img alt="Rated 5 out of 5 stars" src="https://cdn.trustpilot.net/brand-assets/4.1.0/stars/stars-5.svg"/></div></div><div class="styles_reviewContent__tuXiN" aria-hidden="false" data-review-content="true"><a href="/reviews/676893869f6a8f90a5d50e1a" rel="nofollow" target="_self" class="link_internal__Eam_b typography_appearance-inherit__YnCNb link_link__jBdLV link_notUnderlined__y4Qsc" data-review-title-typography="true"><h2 class="typography_heading-xs__osRhC typography_appearance-default__t8iAq" data-service-review-title-typography="true">Zerion is the absolute best of web3, built by the best people.</h2></a><p class="typography_body-l__v5JLj typography_appearance-default__t8iAq" data-service-review-text-typography="true">Zerion is the absolute best in web3, and the only crypto platform I feel safe getting my loved ones onto. Immaculately simple way to access the EVM L2-verse along with mainnet Ethereum needs, and with the launch of their own L2, super excited. <br/><br/>What really makes Zerion special however = the people working on it. Without doxxing anyone, the support teams, the product and marketing teams, have all been incredible whether I have questions or issues or feedback. In app chat support especially shines. <br/><br/>Can’t say enough good stuff about Zerion - the platform has honestly changed my life for the better, protected me from scams, and been a delight to use. </p><p class="typography_body-m__k2UI7 typography_appearance-default__t8iAq" data-service-review-date-of-experience-typography="true"><b class="typography_body-m__k2UI7 typography_appearance-default__t8iAq typography_weight-heavy__rS52U" weight="heavy">Date of experience<!-- -->:</b> <span class="typography_body-m__k2UI7 typography_appearance-subtle__PYOVM">22 December 2024</span></p></div></section></div></article><div data-service-review-stack="true" data-service-review-stack-count="2"><button class="button_button__EM6gX button_s__oTr1f button_appearance-secondary__01O4M button_wide__9LE3T styles_button__dRbZ5" name="review-stack-show" type="button" data-review-stack-show-button="true"><span class="typography_heading-xxxs__SrlLa typography_appearance-inherit__YnCNb typography_disableResponsiveSizing__z3EGy button_buttonText__uWBzs">See 1 more review by Grey<svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="inherit" class="icon_icon__RdICC icon_appearan